These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, airplane
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: peas, apricot
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, fisherman
1. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
4. the fisherman is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Transport   | helicopter     | airplane     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | sprite |
| Food   | peas | apricot  |
| Pet           | horse    | chinchilla |
| Job         | fisherman   | writer       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
City: paris, prague
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, lavender
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, subway
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person who growssunflower is the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person who growssunflower is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| City      | prague    | paris |
| Color           | lavender  | apricot     |
| Flower   | poppy       | sunflower      |
| Transport           | skateboard        | subway      |
| Sport         | volleyball | surfing     |

