.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, romance
House: palace, wooden
City: prague, rome
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, salsa
1. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
2. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching romance movies is the fan of salsa##1
5. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | puzzles    |
| Movie-Genre           | documentary     | romance |
| House   | wooden    | palace   |
| City         | prague | rome   |
| Music-Genre     | trance | salsa |

