.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, fuchsia
2 different games are played: monopoly, chess
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, pop
House: farmhouse, cape-cod
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| Color          | fuchsia     | purple     |
| Game   | monopoly   | chess        |
| Music-Genre   | pop      | blues         |
| House   | cape-cod | farmhouse       |
| Transport         | motorbike  | quad-bike |

