2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
3. the photographer is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Job      | photographer      | dressmaker     |
| Game   | chess    | billiard  |
| Pet           | ferret   | hedgehog |
| Flower         | marigold | sunflower |
| City     | venice     | san-francisco     |

 